import redis from 'redis'

bluebird.promisifyAll(redis)
export default redis.createClient()

import { router } from '../../libs/express'
import { Auth as authController } from '../controller'
import { Auth as authValidate } from '../schemas'

router.route('/')
  .post(authValidate.auth, authController.auth)
